title: HURST VIEW DUB FEST JUNE 2015 - New forest

posts.content:
Hi VW lovers!

Us at Hurst View campsite in Lymington are holding a DubFest on 12th,13th and 14th June 2015 and would love to see you all there!

We're having ferret racing,falcons, food, beer tent, bouncy castle, rodeo bull, disco and campfires!!

Our website is underway however in the meantime have a look at our facebook page for more details
https://www.facebook.com/hurst.view

Be great to hear from you and if anyone knows any trade stands that would be interested give us a message!
